Title: Queen of Katwe - Official Trailer
Comment: HOPE, POWER, COURAGE defined. I've been to the harsh Katwe slum in Kampala. And I've met the courageous chess (and soccer) coach who has mentored Phiona. To overcome the kinds of odds Phiona has overcome is beyond astonishing. The book by Tim Crothers should be on everyone's reading list. Simply to jar us into understanding that we are all more powerful than we think we are. It looks like the movie might rise to the true occasion of what Phiona is still doing to this day. That hope is alive & brilliant especially in the darkest and most ruthless of circumstances.
